notes [-sxi] [-t type] topic1 [...]
.TS
l s
l l.
Everywhere:
?	Help
^D	Leave NOW without sequencer
q,k	Quit
Q,K	Quit without save     
B	Suggestion box
!	Fork shell
.TE
.TS
l s
l l.
Index Page:
+	Forward
*	Last page
-	Backward
\(eq	First page
13	Read note 13 (requires <RET>)
a,A	Search for author
d	Director options
j,J	Jump to first unread note
l,L	Read first unread note or exit
n	Nest notesfiles
o	Oldest date for sequencing
O	Set sequencer time
p	Read policy note
r	Replot the screen
w	Write a note
x,X	Search for title
z	Quit with update
.TE
.TS
l s
l l.
Reading anything:
spc	Next page of current text
-	Previous page of text
ret	Next note
\(eq	Base note
;	Next text
+	Next text
7	Forward 7 responses
|	Pipe text into command
^	Pipe entire note
%	decrypt message (shift 13)
a,A	Search backwards (author)
C	Copy text to notesfile
d	Toggle director message
D	Delete (if yours)
e	Edit title
E	Edit text
i	Index page
j	Next unread text
J	Next unread base note
l	Next new page or exit
L	Next new note or exit
m	Mail to anyone
M	Mail w/text
n	Nest notesfiles
p	Personal note to author
P	To author with text
r	Redraw first page of text
s	Save text
S	Save entire note string
t	Talk to author
w	Write response
x,X	Search backwards (title)
z	Quit with update
Z	Delete (directors only!)
.TE
.TS
l s s
l l l.
Director Options:
a		Toggle anonymous
c		Compress notesfile
n		Toggle network avail.
o		Toggle open status
w		Write policy
z		Zap lots of notes
p		Access (permission) List:
	i	insert
	d	delete
	m	modify
	u	user
	g	group
	s	system
	r	read access
	a	answer access
	d	director options
	w	write access
	n	null access
.TE
